Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,// OPEDC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:06.79,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我们不要被条框锁住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:11.47,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼凑的时光又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:29.97,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了像今天这样的日子才叫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.62,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:40.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了你就能一起踏过所有的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.53,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}恋爱笨蛋 看不清眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手无策 在这深夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:57.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投无路 遵守着约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:03.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己镜中留下投影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:10.14,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我们不要被条框锁住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:14.76,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼凑的时光又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:21.15,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告别 这种答案毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:26.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只会继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:29.95,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:23.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行尸走肉般走过的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:29.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}头顶的阳光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.54,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何时你已经沦落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:40.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}连自己名字也都遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:44.46,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人类 为何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.13,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.04,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}这无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:56.75,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如随之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:57.74,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}无常之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:09.16,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}从寸草不生的山谷向上攀爬 听风带来山林的回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:14.89,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}请看 指引我们的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:20.01,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}就是斩断悲哀的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:24.62,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}别害怕 别颤抖 活下去

